import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Login111 from "./components/web1908/xz/Login111.vue"
import MyHeader from "./components/web1908/xz/MyHeader.vue"
import Index from "./views/Index.vue"
import Carousel from "./components/Index/Carousel.vue"
import Details from "./components/web1908/xz/Details.vue"
import Cart from "./components/web1908/xz/Cart.vue"
import Order from "./components/web1908/xz/Order.vue"

Vue.use(Router)
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/Order',component:Order},
    {path:'/Details',component:Details},
    {path:'/Cart',component:Cart},
    {path:'/Carousel',component:Carousel},
    {path:'/Index',component:Index},
    {path:'/MyHeader',component:MyHeader},
    {path:'/Login111',component:Login111},
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer}
  ]
})
// http://127.0.0.1:8080/#/Exam01
